Tips for text editor and sif files

-----------------------
vim:
-------------------------
syntax file to highlight .sif files

Usage:
make a symbolic link from vim directory to ~/.vim
> ln -s $ElmerIceLGGE/SifEditors/vim ~/.vim

If by default highlithing is off (in foehn for example)
create a ~/.vimrc file and add:
syntax on


